overview: Bring the worlds biggest pot party to your very own living room. The Cannabis Cup 2003 DVD is loaded (just like you) with over 60 minutes of performances, interviews, and non-stop smoking of the biggest and best buds in the world. You’ll laugh, you’ll dance and you’ll want to rip your bong. Relive the magic or see what you missed - this DVD is a must have for any stoner
title: High Times Presents: Cannabis Cup
